{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/about/modern-slavery-statement","content_id":"a820d301-781f-406d-9d80-dcfe820cfc2c","description":"This statement sets out our commitment to identify and tackle modern slavery in our commercial supply chain and in our wider operations.","details":{"attachments":[{"accessible":true,"alternative_format_contact_email":"web.comments@justice.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"6197878c8fa8f50382034d41","filename":"moj-modern-slavery-statement.pdf"},{"asset_manager_id":"6197878c8fa8f503816402da","filename":"thumbnail_moj-modern-slavery-statement.pdf.png"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":3216353,"filename":"moj-modern-slavery-statement.pdf","id":"7552776","number_of_pages":28,"title":"Modern slavery transparency statement 2020 to 2021","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6197878c8fa8f50382034d41/moj-modern-slavery-statement.pdf"},{"accessible":true,"alternative_format_contact_email":"web.comments@justice.gov.uk","assets":[{"asset_manager_id":"61d5667dd3bf7f1f7036fb84","filename":"MoJ-modern-slavery-statement-welsh.pdf"},{"asset_manager_id":"61d5667dd3bf7f1f71aa7d22","filename":"thumbnail_MoJ-modern-slavery-statement-welsh.pdf.png"}],"attachment_type":"file","content_type":"application/pdf","file_size":2134865,"filename":"MoJ-modern-slavery-statement-welsh.pdf","id":"7552777","number_of_pages":35,"title":"Datganiad Tryloywder Caethwasiaeth Fodern y Weinyddiaeth Gyfiawnder 2020-2021","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61d5667dd3bf7f1f7036fb84/MoJ-modern-slavery-statement-welsh.pdf"}],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Building on publication of the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/uk-government-modern-slavery-statement\" class=\"govuk-link\">government modern slavery statement</a> which set out the steps central government has taken to eradicate modern slavery from the domestic and global economy, our first statement captures actions taken to identify, raise awareness and to mitigate modern slavery risks in our department.</p>\n\n<p>It also sets out areas identified for continuous improvement on which we will be able to reflect progress in subsequent years.</p>\n\n<section data-module=\"ga4-link-tracker\" class=\"gem-c-attachment govuk-!-margin-bottom-6\">\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail govuk-!-display-none-print\">\n    <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file_download\",\"type\":\"attachment\"}' href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6197878c8fa8f50382034d41/moj-modern-slavery-statement.pdf\">\n        <svg class=\"gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image gem-c-attachment__thumbnail-image--pdf\" version=\"1.1\" viewbox=\"0 0 99 140\">\n  <path d=\"M12,59h9v9h-9v-9ZM30,77v9h39v-9H30ZM30,104h57v-9H30v9ZM30,122h48v-9H30v9ZM12,86h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,122h9v-9h-9v9ZM12,104h9v-9h-9v9ZM30,68h57v-9H30v9ZM35.2,21c-.3-.2-.6-.4-1-.5s-.8-.2-1.3-.2h-2.6v5.5h2.6c.5,0,1,0,1.3-.2s.7-.3,1-.5c.3-.2.5-.5.7-.8s.2-.7.2-1.1h0c0-.5,0-.9-.2-1.2-.2-.3-.4-.6-.7-.8h0ZM52.4,21.9c-.4-.5-1-.9-1.6-1.1-.7-.3-1.5-.4-2.4-.4h-2.7v11.5h2.7c.9,0,1.7-.1,2.4-.4s1.2-.7,1.6-1.1c.4-.5.7-1.1.9-1.7.2-.7.3-1.4.3-2.1v-.7c0-.8,0-1.5-.3-2.1-.2-.6-.5-1.2-.9-1.7h0ZM87,12v27H12V12h75ZM39.8,23c0-.9-.1-1.6-.4-2.4-.3-.7-.7-1.4-1.2-1.9-.5-.5-1.2-1-1.9-1.2-.8-.3-1.6-.5-2.5-.5h-7.2v17.9h3.6v-6h3.2c.9,0,1.8-.1,2.6-.5.8-.3,1.4-.7,2-1.2.5-.5,1-1.2,1.3-1.9.3-.7.5-1.5.5-2.4h0ZM57.4,26c0-1.3-.2-2.6-.5-3.7s-.9-2-1.6-2.8c-.7-.8-1.6-1.4-2.7-1.8-1.1-.4-2.3-.6-3.8-.6h-6.6v17.9h6.6c1.5,0,2.7-.2,3.8-.6,1.1-.4,2-1,2.7-1.8.7-.8,1.3-1.7,1.6-2.8.4-1.1.5-2.3.5-3.7h0ZM72.4,17.1h-12.1v17.9h3.6v-7.5h7.8v-3.3h-7.8v-3.8h8.4s0-3.3,0-3.3Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n\n</a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"gem-c-attachment__details\">\n    <h2 class=\"gem-c-attachment__title\">\n      <a class=\"govuk-link\" target=\"_self\" data-ga4-link='{\"event_name\":\"file